
Alpha value is used for making colors transparent 
they are shown as percentage and hex is used..

Android supports the #AARRGGBB color format.

A = alpha, R = Red, G = Green, B = Blue

To make some View transparent use #00000000.

First 00 are alpha.


0% = #00
10% = #16
20% = #32
30% = #48
40% = #64
50% = #80
60% = #96
70% = #112
80% = #128
90% = #144
